I'm using vuejs with vue-router and vuex.
I have a module with state, actions and mutations. With actions i call a api and get data from it and change the state by committing mutation. But in my component it doesnot changesm but when i go to another route and come back, it changes.

It's my module:
```const state = {
  info: {
    name: ""
  }
}
const actions = {
  getInfo({ commit }) {
    api.getAllInfo().then((Response) => {
      commit('SET_USER_INFO', Response.data)
    }).catch((err) => {
      console.log(err.response)
    })
  }
const mutations = {
  SET_USER_INFO (state, info) {
    state.info.name = info.name
  }
}```

